<plot>Two hosts run the halls of Denmark's parliamentary building Christiansborg, finding the answers to their questions in informal interviews with politicians and odd-type events to bring smile as well as thought. Each week sees a new political topic and new confrontations of views, and every now and again a controversial happening, topped when a member of parliament was persuaded without much difficulty to perform a body tequila.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?264155</url></doc>
